title: Brighton and Hove Albion vs. Liverpool - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Having lost four of their first five Premier League home games against Liverpool, Brighton are now unbeaten in their last two against the Reds at the Amex Stadium in the competition. Liverpool have won their last two Premier League games against Brighton, having won just one of their previous seven against the Seagulls beforehand.

title: Chelsea vs. Manchester United - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Chelsea have won just one of their last 14 Premier League games against Manchester United, though it was a 4-3 victory in this exact fixture last season. Manchester United have won just one of their last 11 Premier League away games against Chelsea, a 2-0 victory in February 2020 under Ole Gunnar Solskjaer.

title: Everton vs. Southampton - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Everton lost their last home league match against Southampton in January 2023, ending a 17-game unbeaten run against Saints at Goodison Park. They last lost consecutive home league games against them in April 1974. Following their 1-0 win at St Mary’s in the reverse fixture, Southampton are looking to complete the league double over Everton for the first time since 1997-98.

title: Arsenal vs. Newcastle United - English Premier League 2024/2025
description: Arsenal have lost just one of their last 20 Premier League home games against Newcastle, winning 11 of the last 12 since a 1-0 loss in November 2010. Following their 1-0 win at St James’ Park in November, Newcastle are looking to complete their first league double over Arsenal since 1994-95.

title: Ligue 1 Highlights 2024/25 Week 34
description: Each Ligue 1 Match week is condensed into a 52-minute highlights show. Every game, goal, penalty, red card and everything in between is squeezed into an action-packed hour to ensure no football fan misses a kick across the game season.

title: The Final Story: Champions League
description: A host of star names reflect on their experience of some of the greatest Champions League Finals in history,

title: PSG vs Auxerre - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Paris SG have not lost any of their last five matches against Auxerre in Ligue 1. PSG are also unbeaten in their last 37 home games against a promoted side in Ligue 1 – scoring an average of 2.9 goals – since a defeat against Montpellier in their last match of the 2009-10 season. The last draw between Paris SG and Auxerre at the Parc des Princes in Ligue 1 was in December 2001. Since then, the 11 clashes between the two teams in the top-flight have seen eight wins for Paris and three for Auxerre.

title: Metz vs Dunkerque - Ligue 2 playoffs 2024/2025
description: The 2024-25 Ligue 2 is the 44th season of the Ligue 2, the second-tier professional football league in France.18 teams competing in a round-robin format. The top three teams will be promoted to Ligue 1, while the teams finishing 17th and 18th will be relegated to National. AS Monaco, a team with a rich history and a strong fan base, is one of the top contenders to win the championship and earn promotion to the top division.

title: French Ligue 1 2024/25 - Best Goals of Ligue 1
description: Best Goals of Ligue 1 for season 2024/2025.

title: Saint-Étienne vs Toulouse - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: St Etienne have lost only one of their last nine matches against Toulouse in Ligue 1, it was this season in the reverse fixture; a 2-1 win for TFC at home in December. St Etienne have won just one of their last seven matches to finish a Ligue 1 season, 5-0 against Lille in 2017-18.

title: Nantes vs Montpellier - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Nantes have won 64.3% of their Ligue 1 home games against Montpellier in the 21st century, their highest success rate against an opponent they have faced 10+ times on home soil during this period. Since their return to the top-flight in 2013-14, Nantes have finished just two of their last 11 Ligue 1 campaigns with a victory : 1-0 v Strasbourg in 2017-18 and 1-0 v Angers in 2022-23.

description: Extended Highlights - French Ligue 1 2024/25

title: PSG vs Auxerre - Mini Match - French Ligue 1 2024/25
description: Extended Highlights - French Ligue 1 2024/25

title: Lens vs Monaco - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Lens will face Monaco in Ligue 1 for the 108th time, the team that RCL have faced the most in the top-flight but also the one against which they have lost the most, with two defeats in the last three meetings. Lens are unbeaten in their last five matches to finish a Ligue 1 season, two of which came against Monaco. This is the third time in the last five years that the two teams have faced each other at Lens to close their season.

title: Lille vs Reims - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Lille have won two games in a row against Reims in Ligue 1, after failing to win any of the previous four. LOSC could string together three wins against Reims for the second time in their top-flight history, after August 2020-September 2021. Reims have conceded at least one goal in each of their last 13 away games against Lille in Ligue 1, the longest run of its kind for SdR against a current top-flight team.

title: In The Footsteps of Marquinhos - Ligue 1 Documentary 2024/25
description: From Brazil to France, beIN tells you the impressive journey of the Captain of Paris Saint-Germain. With 300 Ligue 1 matches recently played, discover the story of Marquinhos!

title: Olympique Marseille vs Rennes - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: Marseille have won three of their last four home games against Rennes in Ligue 1, each time without conceding a single goal. OM have kept 12 clean sheets at home against SRFC in the 21st century, at least two more than against any other team during this period. Marseille have finished just one of the last 12 Ligue 1 seasons with a defeat, losing 1-0 at Ajaccio on 3 June 2023.

title: Strasbourg vs Le Havre - French Ligue 1 2024/25 Week 34
description: The 39 meetings between Strasbourg and Le Havre in Ligue 1 have produced only three draws, a ratio of 7.7%. This is the lowest percentage of draws between two Ligue 1 teams among those who have faced each other 20+ times. Strasbourg have lost their last three matches to finish a Ligue 1 season, but they have been away from home each time, at Marseille, Lorient and Lyon in the last three years. At home, RCSA have gone three games to close a season without losing.

description: VfL Wolfsburg recorded their joint-biggest win in the Bundesliga this season in the reverse fixture against Borussia Monchengladbach – the Wolves could now do a league double over the Foals for the first time since 2009/10. VfL Wolfsburg are winless in their last nine Bundesliga games, the longest ongoing wait in the league and the Wolves’ longest spell without victory since between December 2023 and March 2024. Wolfsburg are also without a clean sheet in their last 12 Bundesliga matches, currently the worst run in the league.

SC Freiburg have picked up 13 of a possible 15 points over the last five matchdays, a joint league high together with Borussia Dortmund. Eintracht Frankfurt have also remained unbeaten during this period, conceding the joint-fewest goals in the league.

title: Borussia Dortmund vs Holstein Kiel - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: Holstein Kiel and Borussia Dortmund have met three times so far: BVB won 4-0 away in the quarter-finals of the 2011/12 DFB-Pokal and then 5-0 at home in the semi-finals in 2020/21, before the Storks won 4-2 in this season’s reverse fixture. It was Dortmund’s first defeat against a Bundesliga debutant since August 2019. Borussia Dortmund have won four Bundesliga games in a row for the first time since March 2024. title: Mainz 05 vs Bayer Leverkusen - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: 1. FSV Mainz 05 have lost 11 of their 14 Bundesliga games against Bayer 04 Leverkusen since the start of 2018 – the Werkself haven’t beaten any other side more often during this period and the 05ers haven’t suffered more defeats against any other side. Leverkusen have won each of the last three meetings. Bayer 04 Leverkusen have only won one of their last five Bundesliga games. 68 points from 33 games is still their third-best record in the top flight. Last weekend’s 4-2 defeat against Borussia Dortmund saw them concede more than three goals in a Bundesliga game for the first time since October 2022.

title: Bundesliga Highlights 2024/25 Week 34
description: Each Bundesliga Matchweek is condensed into a 52-minute highlights show. Every game, goal, penalty, red card and everything in between is squeezed into an action-packed hour to ensure no football fan misses a kick across the game season.

title: Bundesliga 2024/25 - Goals of Bayern Munich
description: Best Goals of Bayern Munich in season 2024/2025.

title: St. Pauli vs Bochum - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: FC St. Pauli are currently winless in their last six competitive games against VfL Bochum, though they are unbeaten in all five of their top-flight home games against them. St. Pauli haven’t faced any other side as often at home in the Bundesliga without losing at least once. FC St. Pauli are three points and 13 goals ahead of 1. FC Heidenheim going into the final matchday, meaning a point would be enough to guarantee their survival. St. Pauli last avoided relegation in a top-flight season all the way back in 1995/96.

title: Augsburg vs Union Berlin - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 34
description: FC Augsburg have only lost one of their last 11 Bundesliga games against 1. FC Union Berlin and are currently on a longer unbeaten run against Union than versus any other side in the top flight. FCU have only been waiting longer for a Bundesliga win against FC Bayern than versus FCA. FC Augsburg are the only side to have lost each of their last three Bundesliga games – they suffered just one defeat across their previous 14 league outings. FCA have only ever been beaten in more consecutive top-flight fixtures under Jess Thorup across the final five matchdays of last season.

title: Mallorca vs Getafe - LaLiga 2024/25 Week 37
description: Mallorca have not lost any of their last four games against Getafe in LaLiga, equalling their best unbeaten run against them in the top-flight, achieved in their first four meetings between 2004 and 2006. Getafe have taken points in five of their last six LaLiga away games against Mallorca, this after having lost six of their first seven visits to the island in the competition.

description: Race 2 of the Misano weekend intensifies the fight for supremacy in the Italian F4 Championship. Drivers adjust strategies and sharpen their focus after Race 1, aiming to climb the standings in a fast-paced, highly tactical contest under pressure.

description: The final showdown at Misano sees the field go all out in Race 3, where consistency and courage could decide the weekend’s overall winner. With podiums and crucial points at stake, expect a dramatic and decisive finale in this opening round of the 2025 season.

title: Al Ahli (KSA) vs Kawasaki (JPN) - AFC Champions League Elite 2024/25 - Final
description: Al-Ahli will face Kawasaki Frontale for the first time in the AFC Champions League elite and for the first time against a Japanese team. Conversely, this will be Kawasaki Frontales second encounter against a Saudi team after defeating Al-Nassr 3-2 in the semi-finals. Al-Ahli have won only once in 5 matches against East Asian teams, with the win against Shenzhen 2-1 in the 2005 quarter-finals. This will be the fourth final between a Saudi team and a Japanese team in the AFC Champions League elite, the most common final matchup in the tournament. title: St Raphael vs Nantes - LNH Division 1 - French Handball Starligue
description: Dive into the excitement of French handball with Liqui Moly Starligue, formerly LNH Division 1. Established in 1952, this premier league event features 16 top teams battling for glory. With Montpellier’s 14 Handball titles and Paris Saint-Germains 11 wins, the competition is fierce. Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.
